FEATURES INCLUDED (PRO TIER)

- OAuth 2.1 + PKCE authentication
- JWT JWKS mode (auto-refreshing keys for RS256/ES256)
- HTTP transport to upstream MCP servers
- SSE transport for streaming responses
- Per-identity rate limiting

